{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.021.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Achab bless\u00e9 \u00e0 mort dans une exp\u00e9dition contre les Syriens<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-28: cf. 2 Ch 18:1-27. J\u00e9 23:16, 17, 25-32. 2 Ti 4:3. 2 Th 2:11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>On resta trois ans sans qu\u2019il y e\u00fbt guerre entre la Syrie et Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.2","name":"1 Rois 22:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.21.29","name":"1 Rois 21:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.21.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>La troisi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e, Josaphat, roi de Juda, descendit aupr\u00e8s du roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.3","name":"1 Rois 22:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.1","name":"1 Rois 22:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl dit \u00e0 ses serviteurs: Savez-vous que Ramoth en Galaad est \u00e0 nous? Et nous ne nous inqui\u00e9tons pas de la reprendre des mains du roi de Syrie!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.4","name":"1 Rois 22:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.2","name":"1 Rois 22:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et il dit \u00e0 Josaphat: Veux-tu venir avec moi attaquer Ramoth en Galaad? Josaphat r\u00e9pondit au roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Nous irons, moi comme toi, mon peuple comme ton peuple, mes chevaux comme tes chevaux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.5","name":"1 Rois 22:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.3","name":"1 Rois 22:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Puis Josaphat dit au roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Consulte maintenant, je te prie, la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.6","name":"1 Rois 22:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.4","name":"1 Rois 22:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl assembla les proph\u00e8tes, au nombre d\u2019environ quatre cents, et leur dit: Irai-je attaquer Ramoth en Galaad, ou dois-je y renoncer? Et ils r\u00e9pondirent: Monte, et le Seigneur la livrera entre les mains du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.7","name":"1 Rois 22:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.5","name":"1 Rois 22:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Mais Josaphat dit: N\u2019y a-t-il plus ici aucun proph\u00e8te de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, par qui nous puissions le consulter?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.8","name":"1 Rois 22:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.6","name":"1 Rois 22:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Josaphat: Il y a encore un homme par qui l\u2019on pourrait consulter l\u2019\u00c9ternel; mais je le hais, car il ne me proph\u00e9tise rien de bon, il ne proph\u00e9tise que du mal: c\u2019est Mich\u00e9e, fils de Jimla. Et Josaphat dit: Que le roi ne parle pas ainsi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.9","name":"1 Rois 22:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.7","name":"1 Rois 22:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Alors le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl appela un eunuque, et dit: Fais venir de suite Mich\u00e9e, fils de Jimla.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.10","name":"1 Rois 22:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.8","name":"1 Rois 22:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et Josaphat, roi de Juda, \u00e9taient assis chacun sur son tr\u00f4ne, rev\u00eatus de leurs habits royaux, dans la place \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la porte de Samarie. Et tous les proph\u00e8tes proph\u00e9tisaient devant eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.11","name":"1 Rois 22:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.9","name":"1 Rois 22:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>S\u00e9d\u00e9cias, fils de Kenaana, s\u2019\u00e9tait fait des cornes de fer, et il dit: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Avec ces cornes tu frapperas les Syriens jusqu\u2019\u00e0 les d\u00e9truire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.12","name":"1 Rois 22:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.10","name":"1 Rois 22:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Et tous les proph\u00e8tes proph\u00e9tisaient de m\u00eame, en disant: Monte \u00e0 Ramoth en Galaad! Tu auras du succ\u00e8s, et l\u2019\u00c9ternel la livrera entre les mains du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.13","name":"1 Rois 22:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.11","name":"1 Rois 22:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Le messager qui \u00e9tait all\u00e9 appeler Mich\u00e9e lui parla ainsi: Voici, les proph\u00e8tes, d\u2019un commun accord, proph\u00e9tisent du bien au roi; que ta parole soit donc comme la parole de chacun d\u2019eux! Annonce du bien!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.14","name":"1 Rois 22:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.12","name":"1 Rois 22:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Mich\u00e9e r\u00e9pondit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant! J\u2019annoncerai ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel me dira.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.15","name":"1 Rois 22:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.13","name":"1 Rois 22:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019il fut arriv\u00e9 aupr\u00e8s du roi, le roi lui dit: Mich\u00e9e, irons-nous attaquer Ramoth en Galaad, ou devons-nous y renoncer? Il lui r\u00e9pondit: Monte! Tu auras du succ\u00e8s, et l\u2019\u00c9ternel la livrera entre les mains du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.16","name":"1 Rois 22:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.14","name":"1 Rois 22:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et le roi lui dit: Combien de fois me faudra-t-il te faire jurer de ne me dire que la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 au nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.17","name":"1 Rois 22:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.15","name":"1 Rois 22:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Mich\u00e9e r\u00e9pondit: Je vois tout Isra\u00ebl dispers\u00e9 sur les montagnes, comme des brebis qui n\u2019ont point de berger; et l\u2019\u00c9ternel dit: Ces gens n\u2019ont point de ma\u00eetre, que chacun retourne en paix dans sa maison!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.18","name":"1 Rois 22:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.16","name":"1 Rois 22:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl dit \u00e0 Josaphat: Ne te l\u2019ai-je pas dit? Il ne proph\u00e9tise sur moi rien de bon, il ne proph\u00e9tise que du mal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.19","name":"1 Rois 22:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.17","name":"1 Rois 22:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Et Mich\u00e9e dit: \u00c9coute donc la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel! J\u2019ai vu l\u2019\u00c9ternel assis sur son tr\u00f4ne, et toute l\u2019arm\u00e9e des cieux se tenant aupr\u00e8s de lui, \u00e0 sa droite et \u00e0 sa gauche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.20","name":"1 Rois 22:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.18","name":"1 Rois 22:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel dit: Qui s\u00e9duira Achab, pour qu\u2019il monte \u00e0 Ramoth en Galaad et qu\u2019il y p\u00e9risse? Ils r\u00e9pondirent l\u2019un d\u2019une mani\u00e8re, l\u2019autre d\u2019une autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.21","name":"1 Rois 22:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.19","name":"1 Rois 22:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et un esprit vint se pr\u00e9senter devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et dit: Moi, je le s\u00e9duirai. L\u2019\u00c9ternel lui dit: Comment?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.22","name":"1 Rois 22:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.20","name":"1 Rois 22:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Je sortirai, r\u00e9pondit-il, et je serai un esprit de mensonge dans la bouche de tous ses proph\u00e8tes. L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit: Tu le s\u00e9duiras, et tu en viendras \u00e0 bout; sors, et fais ainsi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.23","name":"1 Rois 22:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.21","name":"1 Rois 22:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Et maintenant, voici, l\u2019\u00c9ternel a mis un esprit de mensonge dans la bouche de tous tes proph\u00e8tes qui sont l\u00e0. Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel a prononc\u00e9 du mal contre toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.24","name":"1 Rois 22:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.22","name":"1 Rois 22:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Alors S\u00e9d\u00e9cias, fils de Kenaana, s\u2019\u00e9tant approch\u00e9, frappa Mich\u00e9e sur la joue, et dit: Par o\u00f9 l\u2019esprit de l\u2019\u00c9ternel est-il sorti de moi pour te parler?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.25","name":"1 Rois 22:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.23","name":"1 Rois 22:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Mich\u00e9e r\u00e9pondit: Tu le verras au jour o\u00f9 tu iras de chambre en chambre pour te cacher.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.26","name":"1 Rois 22:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.24","name":"1 Rois 22:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl dit: Prends Mich\u00e9e, et emm\u00e8ne-le vers Amon, chef de la ville, et vers Joas, fils du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.27","name":"1 Rois 22:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.25","name":"1 Rois 22:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Tu diras: Ainsi parle le roi: Mettez cet homme en prison, et nourrissez-le du pain et de l\u2019eau d\u2019affliction, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que je revienne en paix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.28","name":"1 Rois 22:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.26","name":"1 Rois 22:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Et Mich\u00e9e dit: Si tu reviens en paix, l\u2019\u00c9ternel n\u2019a point parl\u00e9 par moi. Il dit encore: Vous tous, peuples, entendez!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.29","name":"1 Rois 22:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.27","name":"1 Rois 22:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.030,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 29-40: cf. 2 Ch 18:28, etc. (1 R 20:34, 42; 21:19.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et Josaphat, roi de Juda, mont\u00e8rent \u00e0 Ramoth en Galaad.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.30","name":"1 Rois 22:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.28","name":"1 Rois 22:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl dit \u00e0 Josaphat: Je veux me d\u00e9guiser pour aller au combat; mais toi, rev\u00eats-toi de tes habits. Et le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl se d\u00e9guisa, et alla au combat.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.31","name":"1 Rois 22:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.29","name":"1 Rois 22:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Le roi de Syrie avait donn\u00e9 cet ordre aux trente-deux chefs de ses chars: Vous n\u2019attaquerez ni petits ni grands, mais vous attaquerez seulement le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.32","name":"1 Rois 22:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.30","name":"1 Rois 22:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Quand les chefs des chars aper\u00e7urent Josaphat, ils dirent: Certainement, c\u2019est le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Et ils s\u2019approch\u00e8rent de lui pour l\u2019attaquer. Josaphat poussa un cri.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.33","name":"1 Rois 22:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.31","name":"1 Rois 22:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Les chefs des chars, voyant que ce n\u2019\u00e9tait pas le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, s\u2019\u00e9loign\u00e8rent de lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.34","name":"1 Rois 22:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.32","name":"1 Rois 22:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.34","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:34","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Alors un homme tira de son arc au hasard, et frappa le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl au d\u00e9faut de la cuirasse. Le roi dit \u00e0 celui qui dirigeait son char: Tourne, et fais-moi sortir du champ de bataille, car je suis bless\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.35","name":"1 Rois 22:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.33","name":"1 Rois 22:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.35","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:35","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Le combat devint acharn\u00e9 ce jour-l\u00e0. Le roi fut retenu dans son char en face des Syriens, et il mourut le soir. Le sang de la blessure coula dans l\u2019int\u00e9rieur du char.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.36","name":"1 Rois 22:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.34","name":"1 Rois 22:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.36","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:36","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Au coucher du soleil, on cria par tout le camp: Chacun \u00e0 sa ville et chacun dans son pays!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.37","name":"1 Rois 22:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.35","name":"1 Rois 22:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.37","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:37","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Ainsi mourut le roi, qui fut ramen\u00e9 \u00e0 Samarie; et on enterra le roi \u00e0 Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.38","name":"1 Rois 22:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.36","name":"1 Rois 22:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.38","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:38","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019on lava le char \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9tang de Samarie, les chiens l\u00e9ch\u00e8rent le sang d\u2019Achab, et les prostitu\u00e9es s\u2019y baign\u00e8rent, selon la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait prononc\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.39","name":"1 Rois 22:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.37","name":"1 Rois 22:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.39","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:39","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Le reste des actions d\u2019Achab, tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, la maison d\u2019ivoire qu\u2019il construisit, et toutes les villes qu\u2019il a b\u00e2ties, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.40","name":"1 Rois 22:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.38","name":"1 Rois 22:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.40","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:40","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Achab se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res. Et Achazia, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.41","name":"1 Rois 22:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.39","name":"1 Rois 22:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.41","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:41","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.042,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Josaphat, roi de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 41-51: cf. (2 Ch 17; 19; 20.) Pr 13:1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>\n    Josaphat, fils d\u2019Asa, r\u00e9gna sur Juda, la quatri\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Achab, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.42","name":"1 Rois 22:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.40","name":"1 Rois 22:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.42","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:42","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Josaphat avait trente-cinq ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna vingt cinq ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Azuba, fille de Schilchi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.43","name":"1 Rois 22:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.41","name":"1 Rois 22:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.43","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:43","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>Il marcha dans toute la voie d\u2019Asa, son p\u00e8re, et ne s\u2019en d\u00e9tourna point, faisant ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.44","name":"1 Rois 22:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.42","name":"1 Rois 22:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.44","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:44","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>Seulement, les hauts lieux ne disparurent point; le peuple offrait encore des sacrifices et des parfums sur les hauts lieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.45","name":"1 Rois 22:45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.43","name":"1 Rois 22:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.45","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:45","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup>Josaphat fut en paix avec le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.46","name":"1 Rois 22:46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.44","name":"1 Rois 22:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.46","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:46","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Josaphat, ses exploits et ses guerres, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois de Juda?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.47","name":"1 Rois 22:47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.45","name":"1 Rois 22:45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.47","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:47","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup>Il \u00f4ta du pays le reste des prostitu\u00e9s, qui s\u2019y trouvaient encore depuis le temps d\u2019Asa, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.48","name":"1 Rois 22:48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.46","name":"1 Rois 22:46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.48","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:48","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup>Il n\u2019y avait point de roi en \u00c9dom: c\u2019\u00e9tait un intendant qui gouvernait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.49","name":"1 Rois 22:49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.47","name":"1 Rois 22:47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.49","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:49","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.050,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup>Josaphat construisit des navires de Tarsis pour aller \u00e0 Ophir chercher de l\u2019or; mais il n\u2019y alla point, parce que les navires se bris\u00e8rent \u00e0 \u00c9tsjon-Gu\u00e9ber.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.50","name":"1 Rois 22:50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.48","name":"1 Rois 22:48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.50","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:50","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.051,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup>Alors Achazia, fils d\u2019Achab, dit \u00e0 Josaphat: Veux-tu que mes serviteurs aillent avec les tiens sur des navires? Et Josaphat ne voulut pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.51","name":"1 Rois 22:51","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.49","name":"1 Rois 22:49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.51","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:51","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.052,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup>Josaphat se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et il fut enterr\u00e9 avec ses p\u00e8res dans la ville de David, son p\u00e8re. Et Joram, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.52","name":"1 Rois 22:52","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.52"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.50","name":"1 Rois 22:50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"52","lastverse":"52","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.52","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.52","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:52","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.051,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.053,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Achazia, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 52-54: cf. 2 R 1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.52\" class=\"v\">52<\/sup>Achazia, fils d\u2019Achab, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Samarie, la dix-septi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de Josaphat, roi de Juda. Il r\u00e9gna deux ans sur Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.53","name":"1 Rois 22:53","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.53"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.51","name":"1 Rois 22:51","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.51"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"53","lastverse":"53","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.53","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.53","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:53","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.052,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.054,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.53\" class=\"v\">53<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il marcha dans la voie de son p\u00e8re et dans la voie de sa m\u00e8re, et dans la voie de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, qui avait fait p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.54","name":"1 Rois 22:54","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.54"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.52","name":"1 Rois 22:52","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.52"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"54","lastverse":"54","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.54","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.54","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 22:54","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.022.053,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.22.54\" class=\"v\">54<\/sup>Il servit Baal et se prosterna devant lui, et il irrita l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, comme avait fait son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22","name":"1 Rois 22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.1.1","name":"2 Rois 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.53","name":"1 Rois 22:53","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.22.53"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb34698f7.08423944');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb34698f7.08423944\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb34698f7.08423944","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb34698f7.08423944'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb34698f7.08423944\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}